{% set father = 'CertUnlpNgenBundle:ExternalIncident:Report/Twig/BaseReport/baseReport.'~txtOrHtml~'.twig' %}
{% extends father %}{% block problem %}

We would like to inform you that we have been notified that the <em>server</em> {{incident.hostAddress}} is currently hosting a web service being used to perform Phising attacks.### [/problem]


{% block derivated_problem_content %}


<p class="lead">Related issues</p>

If this issue is not addressed, the <em>server</em> could be added in public lists of compromised hosts, forcing the web browsers to show security alerts when accessing web pages hosted in the server.


{% endblock %}


{% block verification_content %}


<p class="lead">How to verify the issue</p>

Verify the information in the attached file.


{% endblock %}


{% block recommendations_content %}


<p class="lead">Recommendations</p>

We recommend removing the web content being used to perform the phising attack and request a forensic analysis on the server, as to evaluate what has been compromised.


{% endblock %}


